-What was that?
-Huh?

38:44.322 --> 38:45.932
What do you mean,
"huh"?

38:46.062 --> 38:47.890
Gangbanger funeral
that damn near turned

38:48.021 --> 38:49.588
into yourfuneral.

38:49.718 --> 38:52.547
I-I was mad and --

38:56.464 --> 38:58.074
You know,
I listened to my dad

38:58.205 --> 38:59.815
talk about Michael and --
and it just --

38:59.946 --> 39:02.209
and -- and then,
it made me

39:02.340 --> 39:03.428
just want to go
and take out

39:03.558 --> 39:04.820
every asshole
who had anything to do

39:04.951 --> 39:06.518
with Michael's death,
I want dead.

39:06.648 --> 39:09.651
I know
I'm not supposed to.

39:09.782 --> 39:12.219
You know, the wrong
people stay alive and --

39:14.439 --> 39:15.614
...and the wrong
people die.

39:18.660 --> 39:20.619
So, a bottle of Scotch
on your own?

39:23.883 --> 39:25.363
Maybe once.

39:27.974 --> 39:30.542
But what you really need?

39:30.672 --> 39:32.457
Stay close to the people

39:32.587 --> 39:34.067
who know what you're
going through.

39:34.197 --> 39:36.025
Yeah.

39:36.156 --> 39:38.767
And, if you won't do that,

39:38.898 --> 39:40.290
we'll stay close to you.

39:45.383 --> 39:46.688
Poker night is Wednesday.

40:58.673 --> 40:59.761
You the police?

41:03.417 --> 41:05.550
I'm -- I'm a lawyer.

41:05.680 --> 41:07.160
What kind of lawyer?

41:07.290 --> 41:08.988
Moses Johnson's lawyer.

41:11.730 --> 41:12.861
I saw what happened.

41:19.041 --> 41:20.739
You want to --

41:20.869 --> 41:22.915
You want to talk to me
about that?

41:25.439 --> 41:26.701
Not right here.

41:26.832 --> 41:28.311
O-Okay, okay.

41:30.313 --> 41:31.750
My way of thinking is

41:31.880 --> 41:33.795
cops see Blackness
as a weapon.

41:35.188 --> 41:37.407
Being Black is like,
I don't know,

41:37.538 --> 41:40.236
I might as well have a gun,
you feel me?

41:40.367 --> 41:43.457
So running and fighting,
like Moses did?

41:43.588 --> 41:45.677
That's self-defense.

41:45.807 --> 41:48.810
But they don't see it
like that.

41:48.941 --> 41:50.812
Or they're blind to it.

41:50.943 --> 41:54.947
But the thing to be is
to make the blind see.

41:55.077 --> 41:55.817
You okay?

41:57.036 --> 41:57.732
You sick or something?

41:59.604 --> 42:00.561
Get in here.

42:00.692 --> 42:03.346
Get in here, boy.

42:03.477 --> 42:06.959
"Pursuant
to my attempt to escape,

42:07.089 --> 42:08.526
there was physical contact

42:08.656 --> 42:11.398
between myself
and the police officer,

42:11.529 --> 42:15.097
as a consequence of which
he hit his head."

42:26.456 --> 42:29.242
They think that's
your confession.

42:29.372 --> 42:30.373
It's not.

42:33.115 --> 42:34.552
It's your defense.

43:10.936 --> 43:12.241
Hey, hey, hey.

43:13.895 --> 43:15.505
Here we go!

43:17.551 --> 43:18.334
What's up?

43:26.908 --> 43:28.170
Hey, what you doing?

43:28.301 --> 43:29.084
I know.

43:33.523 --> 43:36.788
I spoke to Dr. Algren.

43:36.918 --> 43:37.615
I know.

44:30.145 --> 44:31.669
On the next episode
of 61st Street...

44:31.799 --> 44:33.758
I have an idea,
and it means you and me

44:33.888 --> 44:36.369
fighting this
and fighting them.

44:36.499 --> 44:39.807
They're gonna come after us
with everything they got.

44:39.938 --> 44:41.504
They comin' for yo ass.

44:41.635 --> 44:43.245
You comin' with us,
you stay alive.

44:43.376 --> 44:44.682
Against the wall.

44:44.812 --> 44:47.119
The question you most want
an answer to is,

44:47.249 --> 44:49.251
"Who killed my son?"
it was me.

44:49.382 --> 44:53.560
Is the law and justice the same
thing? Shouldn't it be?
